{"title":"Android开发-零碎笔记","date":"2018-01-24T09:03:41.000Z","author":"xujiaji","thumbnail":"https://xujiaji.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/blog/android-notes/banner.png","link":"post/android-notes","comments":true,"tags":["Android","笔记"],"categories":["Android"],"updated":"2019-11-27T13:40:17.573Z","content":"<h2 id=\"垂直RecyclerView嵌套垂直RecyclerView滑动时出现的卡顿\">垂直RecyclerView嵌套垂直RecyclerView滑动时出现的卡顿<a href=\"post/android-notes#垂直RecyclerView嵌套垂直RecyclerView滑动时出现的卡顿\"></a></h2><p>原因：内部RecyclerView重复设置适配器导致的卡顿</p>\n<p>解决：判断内部RecyclerView是否设置过适配器，如果没有才设置</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//内部RecyclerView的获取和处理问题的代码</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">RecyclerView rvItem = helper.getView(R.id.rvItem);</span><br><span class=\"line\">rvItem.setNestedScrollingEnabled(<span class=\"keyword\">false</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(rvItem.getAdapter() == <span class=\"keyword\">null</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    LinearLayoutManager layoutManager = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> LinearLayoutManager(mContext);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    layoutManager.setAutoMeasureEnabled(<span class=\"keyword\">true</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    rvItem.setLayoutManager(layoutManager);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    rvItem.setAdapter(<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> OrderItemAdapter(item.getList()));</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"ScrollView嵌套RecyclerView滑动滑动起来很吃力\">ScrollView嵌套RecyclerView滑动滑动起来很吃力<a href=\"post/android-notes#ScrollView嵌套RecyclerView滑动滑动起来很吃力\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">recyclerView.setNestedScrollingEnabled(<span class=\"keyword\">false</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"RecyclerView嵌套RecyclerView时，刷新内部RecyclerView会跳动\">RecyclerView嵌套RecyclerView时，刷新内部RecyclerView会跳动<a href=\"post/android-notes#RecyclerView嵌套RecyclerView时，刷新内部RecyclerView会跳动\"></a></h2><p>原因：内部RecyclerView抢占了焦点</p>\n<p>解决：将内部RecyclerView的焦点设置为false<br><figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">recyclerView.setFocusableInTouchMode(<span class=\"keyword\">false</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<h2 id=\"adb之Wifi连接手机\">adb之Wifi连接手机<a href=\"post/android-notes#adb之Wifi连接手机\"></a></h2><blockquote>\n<p>查看当前设备<code>adb devices</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight sh\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ adb devices</span><br><span class=\"line\">7d1cbcbb\tdevice</span><br><span class=\"line\">192.168.56.101:5555\tdevice</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<blockquote>\n<p>让adb重新启动，并监听端口5555<code>adb -s 设备名 tcpip 5555</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight sh\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ adb -s 7d1cbcbb tcpip 5555</span><br><span class=\"line\">restarting <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> TCP mode port: 5555</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<blockquote>\n<p>连接<code>adb connect ip地址:端口</code>，在手机上查看连接的wifi地址，WiFi需要和电脑网络同网段</p>\n</blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ adb connect 192.168.2.207:5555</span><br><span class=\"line\">connected to 192.168.2.207:5555</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"空包签名\">空包签名<a href=\"post/android-notes#空包签名\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">jarsigner -verbose -keystore [keystore签名秘钥路径] -signedjar [apk输出路径] [apk输入路径（需要签名的空包）] [签名秘钥别名]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"获取签名sha1\">获取签名sha1<a href=\"post/android-notes#获取签名sha1\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">keytool -list -v -keystore [签名路径]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"jadx反编译\">jadx反编译<a href=\"post/android-notes#jadx反编译\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">jadx -d out -j 1 classes.dex</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"Android 无缝换肤深入了解与使用","link":"post/android-skin"},"next":{"title":"HappyBubble-气泡对话框（根据被点击View位置显示、可定制）","link":"post/happy-bubble"},"plink":"https://blog.xujiaji.com/post/android-notes/","toc":[{"title":"垂直RecyclerView嵌套垂直RecyclerView滑动时出现的卡顿","id":"垂直RecyclerView嵌套垂直RecyclerView滑动时出现的卡顿","index":"1"},{"title":"ScrollView嵌套RecyclerView滑动滑动起来很吃力","id":"ScrollView嵌套RecyclerView滑动滑动起来很吃力","index":"2"},{"title":"RecyclerView嵌套RecyclerView时，刷新内部RecyclerView会跳动","id":"RecyclerView嵌套RecyclerView时，刷新内部RecyclerView会跳动","index":"3"},{"title":"adb之Wifi连接手机","id":"adb之Wifi连接手机","index":"4"},{"title":"空包签名","id":"空包签名","index":"5"},{"title":"获取签名sha1","id":"获取签名sha1","index":"6"},{"title":"jadx反编译","id":"jadx反编译","index":"7"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"xujiaji","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow noopener\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","link":"<a href=\"https://blog.xujiaji.com/post/android-notes/\" title=\"Android开发-零碎笔记\">https://blog.xujiaji.com/post/android-notes/</a>"}}